snippet.title: Knightczech: The beginning - Trailer (reupload) (before release)
snippet.description:
First trailer for Knightczech video game.

You may experience few quality drops in the video which I cannot solve. It may be the same issue that is described (questioned and answered) here: https://support.google.com/youtube/thread/2032868?hl=en

You can now wishlist Knightczech on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1382770/Knightczech_The_beginning/


You can also follow the game on social media:

Instagram for new screenshots and game features marked as "work in progress": https://www.instagram.com/knightczechgame/

Facebook page for bigger announcements: https://www.facebook.com/Knightczech

Steam publisher home page: https://store.steampowered.com/curator/38478979/
